<!-- Game Description Table -->

<table class="tablestyle" id="table14" cellspacing="4" cellpadding="0">
	<tr>
		<td class="sectional">

<!-- Game Description Header -->
		
		<table class="headertable" id="table15" cellspacing="2" cellpadding="2">
			<tr>
				<td class="headercell">
				<img border="0" src="../../../images/headers/gamedes.jpg" width="240" height="33"></td>
			</tr>
		</table>

<!-- Game Description Sectional -->

<table border="0" width="100%" id="table16" cellpadding="0">
	<tr>
		<td style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; font-size: 8pt; color: #FFFFFF; font-weight: bold; text-align: left; background-color: #333333; border-left: 2px solid #000000; border-right: 2px solid #FFFFFF; border-top: 2px solid #000000; border-bottom: 2px solid #FFFFFF">
			<br>Super Robot Wars F, is part of the Super Robot Wars franchise, and was published for the PlayStation by Banpresto in 1998. Super Robot Wars F takes place after Super Robot Wars 2, 3, and EX.
			<br><br>STORY:
			<br>After come back from other world called La Girox (Super Robot Wars EX), the war between our heroes, Londo Bell and DC (Divine Crusade) forces excalates. Meanwhile in earth, an organization called Titans formed. It’s purpose is to guard both earth and space colonies even eliminate any of treat if neccesary. However, it’s leader Jamitof Haiman and Treize Khrushnaida seemed had their own intention.
			<br><br>After a few battle with a new enemy called Poseidal forces, Londo Bell meet with Daba Mylord aka King Caman VI, who plan rebellion against Poseidal. He said that Poseidal intention not only his kingdom, Pentagonia but whole galaxy. With assist of Daba Mylord with his friend, the Poseidal army can be stressed. However a new enemy has discover. This time the creatures so called as Shito or Angel can generate a shield (AT Field) so all weapon cannot connect it. Thanks to NERV with his secret weapon Evangelion, the angel can be stopped. To make things more worse, Devil Gundam which known as ultimate gundam fall to the hand of - mad - Kyouji Kashu with strongest martial artist in earth, Tohou Fuhai aka Master Asia at his side. Problem seemed become more complicated when Londo Bell found out that Bystan Well forces lead by the dictator Drake Lust try the same thing as other enemy’s force did.
			<br><br>Londo Bell now find himself defend the earth from never stopped enemy attack, but thanks to many justice motified pilot that decide to help Londo Bell, even with small quantities, the enemy attack can be well stressed. Treize Khrusnaida ask Londo Bell to join Operation Reconqista, a operation to recapture all the base that captured by Guest-Posidal forces. After a succesfull
			<br><br>Operation Reconqista, Treize once again order Londo Bell to investigate a colony occident at outer space. Reach the space, Londo Bell find out that DC is behind everything. Londo Bell also found that leader of Axis base, Haman Karn now is one of main DC General. Can Londo Bell stop the madness of DC forces? Who the 5 mysterious Gundam’s pilot who always disturb Londo Bell? What the true intention of Titans? What is Angel? What the intention of Bystan Well forces? Is mysterious alien known as Guest army behind everything??? Well, keep playing and answer the questions yourself.
			<br><br>SUPER ROBOT WARS F FINAL:
			<br>Super Robot Wars F and F Kanketsuhen tell a combined story, with options to directly continue using already developed characters in the first. Together they wrap up the original Super Robot Taisen, which was continued as Super Robot Taisen Alpha.
			<br><br>GAMEPLAY:
			<br>Super Robot Wars F as the rest of the Banpresto Super Robot Wars games is a Tactical RPG in which the player got a limited range of movement for each of his units and can choose between different attacks when the opponent is in his attack range.
			<br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;<u>Manufacturer's description:</u><br>
                  <br>"Super Robot Taisen F final chapter," appeared in the play station complete with ports? "Final chapter" in the "Legend Ideon ??" Ideon and the "Aim for the Top!" Will appear a number of robots and other stars of the gamba. The story of the robot due to demonstrations starting or union giving the appearance of a DVE system is also the best series climax.
                  <br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;<u>Features:</u><br>
			<ul><li>Third person perspective.</li>
			<li>2D graphics</li>
			<li>Cartoon graphics</li>
			<li>SCI-FI, Futuristic & Anime themes.</li></ul>
</td>

	</tr>
	</table>
	       	</td>
     </tr>
</table>  

